{"tid":609371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"放寬規管 增加植入式廣告 無綫表示歡迎增加廣告收入來源","createTime":"2018-03-29T04:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T11:52:53.000Z","uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbec303f290ef60ea72e3ae815ec94baf71e9cb","tid":609371,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:01:32.000Z","msg":"通訊事務管理局今日起就放寬間接宣傳規管，包括植入式廣告，進行一個月的公眾諮詢。 無綫電視對建議表示歡迎，認為能為廣播業拆牆鬆綁，並會詳細研究諮詢文件。發言人說，通訊局過往極主觀詮釋間接宣傳及植入式廣告的條文，決定亦不一致，將會審視建議能否為持牌機構提供更佳營商環境，以及增加廣告收入來源，特別是細則定義是否更客觀。 有線電視及奇妙電視亦歡迎政府展開諮詢，將積極與當局溝通及研究諮詢文件。"},{"pid":"014c3e591ae0060b5b73dcd51e637371baba4bb1","tid":609371,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979bcc39e88467c29e7564a61adb9aaad7596963","tid":609371,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"am730  頭條日報化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add6083f88fd20d75ee4639495b7d2d246e8a1a6","tid":609371,"uid":5793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:05:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母個東張西望成集都賣廣告架啦屌<br />\n仲cap唔夠水"},{"pid":"5f8bd4865d54d198e35e7e855256c8e1ddba1417","tid":609371,"uid":76063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"放寬只會更少人睇"},{"pid":"ca7deb5ecb47e18ba715a247ea9de70c31e9608f","tid":609371,"uid":143915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"冇人睇，你仲有撚廣告咩，垃圾無綫，鬆章比你想你吊多幾年命咋"},{"pid":"de1d74c86365c17d0ec9de74b016c770deaec0b6","tid":609371,"uid":91633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"根本殺雞取卵行為本倒置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd34ba161e21f220c7be3a0a1ba792e00af00fb","tid":609371,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:2